snippet.textDisplay: On repeat...love this.  Love Sindh.  Love the simplicity, the purity, the uplifting love oozing out of the words and the voices of this trio.  The best of this season because it is closest to our roots - it is authentic.  These sounds, these voices are becoming rarer as modern music takes over.  It is great to hear our music.  Thank you Coke Studio.
